title: FALLING FOR FOLIAGE | News | indianagazette.com
text: The Kintersburg covered bridge over Crooked Creek in Rayne Township was surrounded by fall foliage on Friday. The Indiana Gazette is accepting submission for an online fall foliage photo gallery. A mix of clouds and sun during the morning will give way to cloudy skies this afternoon. High 67F. Winds WSW at 5 to 10 mph.. Partly cloudy skies this evening will become overcast overnight. Slight chance of a rain shower. Low 54F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph.
